                    </p>
                </div>

                        <span class="newspaper_entry_font">Zasady gry:</span>
                        <br>
                        Pewne zasady muszą być przestrzegane, aby gra w Supremacy 1914 była przyjemna, jak to tylko możliwe, dla każdego.
                        <span class="newspaper_url clickable" id="func_button_rules">Zapoznaj się z zasadami gry</span>
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="func_beginners_guide_section" data-guide-type="faq">
                    <p class="clearfix">
                        <span class="newspaper_entry_font">FAQ:</span>
                        <br>
                        Jeśli nadal masz pytania, kliknij na link na końcu, aby zapoznać się z najczęstszymi pytaniami i odpowiedziami na nie. Możesz także zapytać innych graczy na forach lub czacie gry.
                        <span class="newspaper_url clickable" id="func_button_faq">Przeczytaj FAQ</span>
                    </p>
                </div>

                        <br>
                        </p><ul class="newspaper_hint_list">

                                Możesz wyszukiwać prowincje za pomocą kombinacji klawiszy CTRL + F
                            </li>

                            </li>
                            <li>

                            </li>
                        </ul>

                        <div class="padding_top_small"></div>
                        <div class="separator_horizontal"></div>
                        <div class="padding_bottom_small"></div>

                        </div>
                    
                    <div class="article_body_text">
                        I'm sorry to hear that you feel the Rio Alliance is waffling. However, I assure you that our coalition takes our mission very seriously and we are committed to achieving our goals.<br>
<br>
Our detailed communication and planning are necessary to ensure that all members of our alliance are on the same page and working towards the same objectives. We believe that open communication, collaboration, and mutual respect are key to achieving success.<br>
<br>
We recognize that each member of our alliance brings unique strengths and perspectives, and we value the diversity of thought and ideas within our coalition. This is why we take the time to carefully consider all viewpoints and ensure that we are making decisions that are in the best interest of all members of our alliance.<br>
<br>
I understand that our detailed communication may seem excessive to some, but we believe that it is necessary to achieve our goals and ensure the success of all members of our coalition.<br>
<br>
Thank you for your feedback, and we welcome any suggestions or ideas you may have to help us improve our communication and collaboration.<br>
<br>
Sincerely,<br>
<br>
Luntik420&nbsp;

<br>

8:37 pm The 7th  Infantry Division (<span class="func_country_link clickable" data-player-id="17">Essex &amp; Suffolk</span>) has captured <span class="func_provLink clickable " style="text-decoration: underline;" data-prov-name="Oxford">Oxford</span>.<br>
9:49 pm <span class="func_provLink clickable " style="text-decoration: underline;" data-prov-name="Oxford">Oxford</span>: The 3rd  Infantry Brigade (<span class="func_country_link clickable" data-player-id="18">Gloucestershire &amp; Oxfordshire</span>) (R 3) has been destroyed.<br>
10:34 pm <span class="func_provLink clickable " style="text-decoration: underline;" data-prov-name="Oxford">Oxford</span>: The 4th  Infantry Brigade (<span class="func_country_link clickable" data-player-id="18">Gloucestershire &amp; Oxfordshire</span>) (R 4) has been destroyed.<br>
<br>

<span class="func_country_link clickable" data-player-id="18">Gloucestershire &amp; Oxfordshire</span> - 17,000<br>

                    <div class="article_title_and_info">
                        <div class="article_title"><h2>Round Started</h2></div>
                        <div class="padding_top_small"></div>
                        <div class="separator_horizontal"></div>
                        <div class="padding_bottom_small"></div>
                        <div><span class="func_country_link clickable" data-player-id="-1"></span>: Oficjalny komunikat rządu , 07:01</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="article_body">
                    
                    <div class="article_body_text">
                        The round has started. From now on leaders can issue orders to all of their departments.<br>
As rough times lay ahead, the statesmen are advised to look out for allies. This can help in times of war and meeting their people's needs of basic resources.<br>
Open slots can still be taken by new players during the next days.&nbsp;
